Oh boy, my first art exchange!

This was my pinch hit for [[*User Jack Ike]]! One of their requests was to draw one of their characters, so I chose to draw Royoto Hishakaku from [[[SCP-6488]]]. 

Huge thanks to [[*User nomoretears]], who helped me design this interpretation of Hishakaku. I seriously wouldn't have been able to do this without you.
